official_title: A bill to provide for conveyance of certain mineral interests of the United States in real property situated in Florida to the record owners of the surface of that property.

summary.text: Provides for conveyance of mineral interests of the United States in real property situated in Florida to the record owners of the surface of that property in the Tallahassee, Florida area.
